{"calories":"820","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"When we think of the ideal summery sandwich, a cheesy, tomatoey Caprese sandwich always pops into our heads. Here, we’re taking things to next level deliciousness, combining insanely creamy burrata cheese and a saucy double tomato filling on pesto-slicked sourdough. Did we mention that the panini is cooked to prime gooeyness and served with a refreshing arugula salad? Forgive us, we were just begging the test kitchen for a sample. ","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"ae5653c64c","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13369/buratta_panini_mobile.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/hero_buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/menu_small_buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/small_square_buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/medium_square_buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13371/recipe_profile_page_buratta_panini_hero.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13370/buratta_panini_thumb.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/13370/menu_small_buratta_panini_thumb.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Tomato and Burrata Panini with Pesto and Arugula Salad","novice_time":"","portion_count":2,"prep_time":"30-40","pro_time":"","product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"tomato-and-burrata-panini-with-pesto-and-arugula-salad","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/7429/recipe_card20160718-3-1cq7d9p.pdf","recipe_id":1535,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Tomato and Burrata Panini","subtitle":"with Pesto and Arugula Salad","title":"Tomato and Burrata Panini","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"Be sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us–you'll be glad you did!\n\nBurrata is a very delicate cheese so be sure to handle gently. Since it is filled with a soft cream, discard only the watery liquid from container and not any cheese solids!\n\nTo check if the pan is hot enough, simply hover your hand a few inches away from the pan. If it's hot enough, you'll be able to feel the heat. ","equipment":["12\" large nonstick pan with lid"],"id":1535,"ingredients":["vine-ripe tomatoes","grape tomatoes","garlic","red onion","burrata","sherry vinegar","sourdough bread","pesto","balsamic vinegar","sugar","baby arugula"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"vine-ripe tomatoes","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1376/medium_square_medium_square_tomato-2-new.jpg"},{"name":"grape tomatoes","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/191/medium_square_GRAPE_TOMATOES_copy.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"red onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/90/medium_square_red-onion-cut-half.jpg"},{"name":"burrata","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1087/medium_square_medium_square_fresh_mozzarella.jpg"},{"name":"sherry vinegar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/313/medium_square_SHERRY_VINEGAR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"sourdough bread","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"slice","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/45/medium_square_SOUR_DOUGH.jpg"},{"name":"pesto","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1075/medium_square_PESTO_-4396_copy.jpg"},{"name":"balsamic vinegar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/3/medium_square_BALSAMIC_VINEGAR0019.jpg"},{"name":"sugar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/292/medium_square_sugar-test.jpg"},{"name":"baby arugula","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/239/medium_square_arugula-test.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"4.5","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11765/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients4.jpg","description":"Rinse all produce. Roughly chop \u003cb\u003evine-ripe tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e, and halve \u003cb\u003egrape tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e. Mince \u003cb\u003egarlic\u003c/b\u003e. Peel \u003cb\u003ered onion\u003c/b\u003e, halve, and thinly slice as much as desired. Remove \u003cb\u003eburrata\u003c/b\u003e from container and set aside in a small bowl, discarding excess liquid (see Recipe Tip)."},{"title":"Cook Tomatoes","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11766/recipe_card_size_2._Cook_Tomatoes.jpg","description":"Heat \u003cb\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e in a large nonstick pan over medium-high heat.  When oil is shimmering, add \u003cb\u003echopped tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003egarlic\u003c/b\u003e and cook until tomatoes have softened, 3-4 minutes.  Stir in \u003cb\u003esherry vinegar\u003c/b\u003e and season with \u003cb\u003e.125 teaspoon salt\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e as desired.  Remove \u003cb\u003etomatoes\u003c/b\u003e from pan and set aside to cool."},{"title":"Toast Bread","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/12111/recipe_card_size_3._Toast_Bread_2.jpg","description":"Wipe pan from tomatoes clean and place over medium heat.  Drizzle \u003cb\u003e1.5 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/b\u003e over both sides of bread slices, dividing evenly. Add \u003cb\u003ebread\u003c/b\u003e to pan and toast until golden, about 3 minutes per side. Remove from pan and set aside. "},{"title":"Assemble Paninis","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11768/recipe_card_size_4._Assemble_Panini.jpg","description":"Place \u003cb\u003ebread slices\u003c/b\u003e on a clean dry surface, then spread with \u003cb\u003epesto\u003c/b\u003e, dividing evenly. Top 1 side of sandwich with \u003cb\u003ecooked tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e and top with \u003cb\u003eburrata\u003c/b\u003e, dividing evenly. Finish with \u003cb\u003eremaining bread\u003c/b\u003e pesto-side down.\n"},{"title":"Cook Paninis \u0026 Make Dressing","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11769/recipe_card_size_5._Cook_Panini.jpg","description":"Return pan to medium heat. When pan is hot, add \u003cb\u003epaninis\u003c/b\u003e and cover pan (see Recipe Tip). Cook until cheese is warmed through, about 3 minutes total. While paninis cook, in a large bowl, whisk together \u003cb\u003ebalsamic vinegar\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003esugar\u003c/b\u003e, and \u003cb\u003e2 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/b\u003e until dressing comes together and oil is emulsified. Season with \u003cb\u003e.125 teaspoon salt\u003c/b\u003e and \u003cb\u003epepper\u003c/b\u003e as desired. "},{"title":"Plate Paninis ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/11770/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Paninis_2.jpg","description":"Add \u003cb\u003earugula\u003c/b\u003e, \u003cb\u003egrape tomatoes\u003c/b\u003e, and \u003cb\u003eonion\u003c/b\u003e to bowl with \u003cb\u003ebalsamic dressing\u003c/b\u003e and toss to coat.  Divide \u003cb\u003esalad\u003c/b\u003e between two plates and serve with \u003cb\u003eburrata paninis\u003c/b\u003e. Delight in your blissful, cheesy dinner. "}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"test kitchen pick","slug":"test-kitchen-pick","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Bread","slug":"bread","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"test kitchen pick","slug":"test-kitchen-pick","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}